Nevermind, I think the issue is that this API-to-state mapper actually omits `cancellable`

```
function transformTasks(tasks) {
  return tasks.map(task => ({
    id: task.id,
    type: task.type,
    status: task.status,
    metadata: task.metadata,
    percentage: task.percentage,
  }));
}

```

